## Context

ZeisWorks is a solo technical consulting business run by Jack Zeis, based in Golden, CO. The service model is diagnostic-first: clients submit any operational business problem for free, receive an actionable plain-English plan within 24 hours at no cost, and only pay if they want Jack to execute the plan. The target client is a traditional business owner — fewer than 100 employees, trades/professional services/healthcare/manufacturing — who is skeptical of technology consultants, has likely been burned before, and does not have an in-house IT person.

The site is a single-page HTML site. Three specific improvements are required based on a design and conversion research review. Do not alter any other sections, copy, layout, or design elements outside of what is specified below.

