## Change 1: Upwork Badge — Add Hyperlink

### What to change
The existing "100% Job Success · Top Rated on Upwork" badge in the Client Reviews section currently has no link. Make the badge a hyperlink.

### Specification
- **Link destination:** `https://www.upwork.com/freelancers/~01ddd112c03a2e1428`
- **Opens in:** New tab (`target="_blank"` with `rel="noopener noreferrer"`)
- **Visual treatment:** No change to the badge appearance. No underline. No arrow or external link icon. The badge should not visually signal that it is clickable — it functions as a quiet verification link for visitors who choose to investigate, not as a prompt to leave the site.
- **Cursor:** `cursor: pointer` on hover is sufficient.

